{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1046,"text":"One billion people in the world today"},{"time":3565,"text":"do not have access to all-season roads."},{"time":5845,"text":"One billion people."},{"time":7550,"text":"One seventh of the Earth's population"},{"time":9721,"text":"are totally cut off for some part of the year."},{"time":13030,"text":"We cannot get medicine to them reliably,"},{"time":15358,"text":"they cannot get critical supplies,"},{"time":17704,"text":"and they cannot get their goods to market"},{"time":19693,"text":"in order to create a sustainable income."},{"time":23583,"text":"In sub-Saharan Africa, for instance,"},{"time":25727,"text":"85 percent of roads are unusable in the wet season."},{"time":29640,"text":"Investments are being made,"},{"time":31659,"text":"but at the current level,"},{"time":33204,"text":"it's estimated it's going to take them"},{"time":34601,"text":"50 years to catch up."},{"time":37707,"text":"In the U.S. alone, there's more than four million"},{"time":40001,"text":"miles of roads, very expensive to build,"},{"time":43132,"text":"very expensive to maintain infrastructure,"},{"time":46503,"text":"with a huge ecological footprint,"},{"time":48772,"text":"and yet, very often, congested."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52444,"text":"So we saw this and we thought,"},{"time":54826,"text":"can there be a better way?"},{"time":56309,"text":"Can we create a system using today's\nmost advanced technologies"},{"time":59764,"text":"that can allow this part of the world to leapfrog"},{"time":62884,"text":"in the same way they've done with mobile telephones"},{"time":65239,"text":"in the last 10 years?"},{"time":67114,"text":"Many of those nations have excellent telecommunications today"},{"time":70059,"text":"without ever putting copper lines in the ground."},{"time":73036,"text":"Could we do the same for transportation?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76386,"text":"Imagine this scenario."},{"time":78701,"text":"Imagine you are in a maternity ward in Mali,"},{"time":81859,"text":"and have a newborn in need of urgent medication."},{"time":85089,"text":"What would you do today?"},{"time":87321,"text":"Well, you would place a request via mobile phone,"},{"time":89718,"text":"and someone would get the request immediately."},{"time":92582,"text":"That's the part that works."},{"time":94575,"text":"The medication may take days to arrive, though,"},{"time":96612,"text":"because of bad roads."},{"time":98022,"text":"That's the part that's broken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100378,"text":"We believe we can deliver it within hours"},{"time":102895,"text":"with an electric autonomous flying vehicle"},{"time":105476,"text":"such as this."},{"time":106881,"text":"This can transport a small payload\ntoday, about two kilograms,"},{"time":109766,"text":"over a short distance, about 10 kilometers,"},{"time":112400,"text":"but it's part of a wider network that may cover"},{"time":114755,"text":"the entire country, maybe even the entire continent."},{"time":118715,"text":"It's an ultra-flexible, automated logistics network."},{"time":123053,"text":"It's a network for a transportation of matter."},{"time":125988,"text":"We call it Matternet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127765,"text":"We use three key technologies."},{"time":129279,"text":"The first is electric autonomous flying vehicles."},{"time":131914,"text":"The second is automated ground stations"},{"time":134625,"text":"that the vehicles fly in and out of"},{"time":136604,"text":"to swap batteries and fly farther,"},{"time":138862,"text":"or pick up or deliver loads."},{"time":140604,"text":"And the third is the operating system"},{"time":142335,"text":"that manages the whole network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145078,"text":"Let's look at each one of those\ntechnologies in a bit more detail."},{"time":148417,"text":"First of all, the UAVs."},{"time":150662,"text":"Eventually, we're going to be\nusing all sorts of vehicles"},{"time":152746,"text":"for different payload capacities and different ranges."},{"time":155200,"text":"Today, we're using small quads."},{"time":157456,"text":"These are able to transport two kilograms"},{"time":159799,"text":"over 10 kilometers in just about 15 minutes."},{"time":162612,"text":"Compare this with trying to trespass a bad road"},{"time":165138,"text":"in the developing world,"},{"time":166552,"text":"or even being stuck in traffic"},{"time":168772,"text":"in a developed world country."},{"time":170817,"text":"These fly autonomously."},{"time":172527,"text":"This is the key to the technology."},{"time":174083,"text":"So they use GPS and other sensors on board"},{"time":176443,"text":"to navigate between ground stations."},{"time":180137,"text":"Every vehicle is equipped with an automatic"},{"time":182562,"text":"payload and battery exchange mechanism,"},{"time":185600,"text":"so these vehicles navigate to those ground stations,"},{"time":188006,"text":"they dock, swap a battery automatically,"},{"time":190122,"text":"and go out again."},{"time":191826,"text":"The ground stations are located on safe locations"},{"time":194582,"text":"on the ground."},{"time":196144,"text":"They secure the most vulnerable part of the mission,"},{"time":198143,"text":"which is the landing."},{"time":199997,"text":"They are at known locations on the ground,"},{"time":202089,"text":"so the paths between them are also known,"},{"time":204009,"text":"which is very important from a reliability perspective"},{"time":206747,"text":"from the whole network."},{"time":208298,"text":"Apart from fulfilling the energy\nrequirements of the vehicles,"},{"time":211122,"text":"eventually they're going to be becoming"},{"time":213494,"text":"commercial hubs where people can take out loads"},{"time":216194,"text":"or put loads into the network."},{"time":219257,"text":"The last component is the operating system"},{"time":221480,"text":"that manages the whole network."},{"time":223374,"text":"It monitors weather data from all the ground stations"},{"time":226115,"text":"and optimizes the routes of\nthe vehicles through the system"},{"time":229456,"text":"to avoid adverse weather conditions,"},{"time":232047,"text":"avoid other risk factors,"},{"time":234050,"text":"and optimize the use of the resources"},{"time":235770,"text":"throughout the network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237668,"text":"I want to show you what one of those flights"},{"time":239310,"text":"looks like."},{"time":241078,"text":"Here we are flying in Haiti last summer,"},{"time":245020,"text":"where we've done our first field trials."},{"time":247463,"text":"We're modeling here a medical delivery"},{"time":249607,"text":"in a camp we set up after the 2010 earthquake."},{"time":254447,"text":"People there love this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256998,"text":"And I want to show you"},{"time":259127,"text":"what one of those vehicles looks like up close."},{"time":264003,"text":"So this is a $3,000 vehicle."},{"time":266011,"text":"Costs are coming down very rapidly."},{"time":270028,"text":"We use this in all sorts of weather conditions,"},{"time":273203,"text":"very hot and very cold climates,"},{"time":274998,"text":"very strong winds. They're very sturdy vehicles."},{"time":281096,"text":"Imagine if your life depended on this package,"},{"time":285115,"text":"somewhere in Africa"},{"time":286559,"text":"or in New York City, after Sandy."},{"time":290822,"text":"The next big question is, what's the cost?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":294128,"text":"Well, it turns out that the cost to transport"},{"time":297938,"text":"two kilograms over 10 kilometers with this vehicle"},{"time":301897,"text":"is just 24 cents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305270,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310342,"text":"And it's counterintuitive, but the cost of energy"},{"time":313086,"text":"expended for the flight is only two cents"},{"time":315075,"text":"of a dollar today,"},{"time":316413,"text":"and we're just at the beginning of this."},{"time":318546,"text":"When we saw this, we felt that this is something"},{"time":321148,"text":"that can have significant impact in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324147,"text":"So we said, okay, how much does it cost"},{"time":326565,"text":"to set up a network somewhere in the world?"},{"time":328633,"text":"And we looked at setting up a network in Lesotho"},{"time":330663,"text":"for transportation of HIV/AIDS samples."},{"time":333704,"text":"The problem there is how do you take them"},{"time":336111,"text":"from clinics where they're being collected"},{"time":338340,"text":"to hospitals where they're being analyzed?"},{"time":341360,"text":"And we said, what if we wanted to cover an area"},{"time":343502,"text":"spanning around 140 square kilometers?"},{"time":346159,"text":"That's roughly one and a half times\nthe size of Manhattan."},{"time":349633,"text":"Well it turns out that the cost to do that there"},{"time":351800,"text":"would be less than a million dollars."},{"time":354775,"text":"Compare this to normal infrastructure investments."},{"time":358006,"text":"We think this can be -- this is the power"},{"time":361163,"text":"of a new paradigm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363882,"text":"So here we are: a new idea"},{"time":366365,"text":"about a network for transportation"},{"time":368235,"text":"that is based on the ideas of the Internet."},{"time":370881,"text":"It's decentralized, it's peer-to-peer,"},{"time":373110,"text":"it's bidirectional, highly adaptable,"},{"time":375813,"text":"with very low infrastructure investment,"},{"time":378323,"text":"very low ecological footprint."},{"time":382456,"text":"If it is a new paradigm, though,"},{"time":384740,"text":"there must be other uses for it."},{"time":386886,"text":"It can be used perhaps in other places in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389052,"text":"So let's look at the other end of the spectrum:"},{"time":393230,"text":"our cities and megacities."},{"time":395235,"text":"Half of the Earth's population lives in cities today."},{"time":398107,"text":"Half a billion of us live in megacities."},{"time":400827,"text":"We are living through an amazing urbanization trend."},{"time":403507,"text":"China alone is adding a megacity"},{"time":405480,"text":"the size of New York City every two years."},{"time":408587,"text":"These are places that do have road infrastructure,"},{"time":411240,"text":"but it's very inefficient."},{"time":413554,"text":"Congestion is a huge problem."},{"time":415686,"text":"So we think it makes sense in those places"},{"time":417626,"text":"to set up a network of transportation"},{"time":419996,"text":"that is a new layer that sits between the road"},{"time":422162,"text":"and the Internet,"},{"time":423433,"text":"initially for lightweight, urgent stuff,"},{"time":426339,"text":"and over time, we would hope to develop this"},{"time":428388,"text":"into a new mode of transportation"},{"time":430380,"text":"that is truly a modern solution to a very old problem."},{"time":433832,"text":"It's ultimately scalable"},{"time":435386,"text":"with a very small ecological footprint,"},{"time":438244,"text":"operating in the background 24/7,"},{"time":441220,"text":"just like the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443566,"text":"So when we started this"},{"time":445988,"text":"a couple of years ago now,"},{"time":448990,"text":"we've had a lot of people come up to us who said,"},{"time":451334,"text":"\"This is a very interesting but crazy idea,"},{"time":454166,"text":"and certainly not something that you should"},{"time":456000,"text":"engage with anytime soon.\""},{"time":458714,"text":"And of course, we're talking about drones, right,"},{"time":460857,"text":"a technology that's not only unpopular in the West"},{"time":464559,"text":"but one that has become a very, very unpleasant"},{"time":466507,"text":"fact of life for many living in poor countries,"},{"time":469372,"text":"especially those engaged in conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472183,"text":"So why are we doing this?"},{"time":476717,"text":"Well, we chose to do this one"},{"time":479501,"text":"not because it's easy,"},{"time":481287,"text":"but because it can have amazing impact."},{"time":484122,"text":"Imagine one billion people being connected"},{"time":486947,"text":"to physical goods in the same way"},{"time":489342,"text":"that mobile telecommunications connected them"},{"time":492366,"text":"to information."},{"time":494458,"text":"Imagine if the next big network we built in the world"},{"time":498198,"text":"was a network for the transportation of matter."},{"time":501961,"text":"In the developing world, we would hope"},{"time":504363,"text":"to reach millions of people with better vaccines,"},{"time":507068,"text":"reach them with better medication."},{"time":508952,"text":"It would give us an unfair advantage against battling"},{"time":510810,"text":"HIV/AIDS, tuberculosis and other epidemics."},{"time":514802,"text":"Over time, we would hope it would become"},{"time":516498,"text":"a new platform for economic transactions,"},{"time":518672,"text":"lifting millions of people out of poverty."},{"time":521133,"text":"In the developed world and the emerging world,"},{"time":523343,"text":"we would hope it would become a new mode"},{"time":524811,"text":"of transportation that could help make our cities"},{"time":528532,"text":"more livable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530385,"text":"So for those that still believe\nthat this is science fiction,"},{"time":533728,"text":"I firmly say to you that it is not."},{"time":536543,"text":"We do need to engage, though,"},{"time":538212,"text":"in social fiction to make it happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541280,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543447,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}